gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Holiday of Diwali for eight days, Ramnavmi for Shivaratri; 
Victory victory on Akadashi, redemption from sin and sorrow.

Child of Joban, old man and young woman,
No one is staying at home in shame; 
Narayanan saw, four castes came, four hermits.

Here is the translation:

On my head a beautiful crown is placed, if one does not see it; 
such a statue will be revealed, they will call out to you with a sweet name.
